high_descs: Turn around, head towards the sink, and then turn right towards the counter.
Pick up the fork from the counter.
Turn around and head towards the microwave on the counter.
Place the fork in the bowl inside the microwave.
Take out the bowl with the fork from the microwave.
Turn left to face the glass vase on the counter.
Place the bowl on the right side of the glass vase.
anns.task_desc: Place the bowl with a fork on the right side of the glass vase on the counter.

high_descs: Turn right and walk towards the sink then turn left and walk to the counter.
Pick up the fork on the counter.
Turn right and walk towards the microwave.
Open the microwave and place the fork inside of the bowl that is inside the microwave.
Take the bowl with the fork in it out of the microwave.
Close the microwave door and turn to the left.
Place the bowl with the fork inside to the right of the bottle and potato.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl with a fork in it on the counter next to the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the sink then turn left and walk to the counter.
Pick up the fork to the left of the yellow handled knife.
Turn around and walk to the microwave you see in front of you and stand in front of it facing it.
Put the fork in the clear bowl.
Pick up the clear bowl with the fork in it and close the microwave.
Turn left.
Put the bowl between the potato and bottle but slightly to the right of them.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl with a fork in it on the counter.
